==English==
===Noun===
'''Ethernet'''
# A set of network cabling and network access protocol ([[CSMA/CD]]) standards for [[bus topology]] computer networks invented by Xerox but now controlled by the 802.3 subcommittee of the [[IEEE]].
# A computer network which complies with such set of standards.

